{"tid":1531650,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我宣布從今日開始每日都係全民運動日","createTime":"2019-09-02T09:46:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T19:56:12.000Z","uid":313127,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"33e0b6ee51a327356c72ed8cca4f88abcc7f2d76","tid":1531650,"uid":313127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:46:56.000Z","msg":"CD-ROM第一次出post有咩做得唔好大家屌輕手啲。<br />\n大家睇下呢張圖有咩問題？？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cjm7o2w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcjm7o2w.png&h=dd21b615&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">天下武功</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">無堅不破</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唯快不破</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家必須認清香港已經進入緊急狀態<br />\n港共政權既濫捕只會更加變本加厲<br />\n眼見好多手足體力真係有極大提升<br />\n但我地每次購物環境就越黎越惡劣<br />\n所以<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">體力</span></span>真係好重要<br />\n<br />\n無論你係<span style=\"color: gold;\">前線</span>定係<span style=\"color: violet;\">和理非</span><br />\n戰場之上有太多野要幫手<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><br />\n每人既裝備<br />\n物資運送<br />\n人手一枝鹽水ready<br />\n極短時間轉場/撤離<br />\n比狗追反追狗<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n呢啲都需要<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">體力</span></span><br />\n<br />\n老毛講過：身體是革命的本錢<br />\n<br />\n所以我地更加要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">運動運動運動</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n我提議！！！<br />\n由今日開始<br />\n大家每晚<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">9點落樓跑步</span><br />\n跑到鳩叫演唱會作完結<br />\n<br />\n善用日常時間<br />\n有樓梯就盡量行樓梯<br />\n翻20樓就18樓行上去<span style=\"color: pink;\">每日行多一層</span><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\">點燃狼煙，敲響戰鼓，以十為伍，會百成軍，以血和汗鍛體，以死與生滌心，光復香港，時代革命。</span>"},{"pid":"40a55d9e6307f04c6bb802783198ba2272335112","tid":1531650,"uid":313127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:48:01.000Z","msg":"自推十連一"},{"pid":"1f9aad59d0fd2da77ffff40bccd7651f76d3ee49","tid":1531650,"uid":313127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:48:26.000Z","msg":"自推十連二"},{"pid":"2b58d0a9f885069ee84587d827d7a51a034472f8","tid":1531650,"uid":313127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:02:39.000Z","msg":"自推十連三"},{"pid":"d8b28b1f4551512117bea8761b0ec9c489a206b0","tid":1531650,"uid":313127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:05:39.000Z","msg":"自推十連四"},{"pid":"a116c213ee46599d02a81e022e1a885988d508d8","tid":1531650,"uid":313127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:29:26.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4bd48c6fba8180c082c48ffee709efba8db1975","tid":1531650,"uid":313127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T19:56:12.000Z","msg":"721唔見人<br />\n831打死人"}]}